Descriptor.0: ect-hope-L3>ECT Helium Oxygen Proton Electron Plasma Analyszer Level 3

Logical_source_description.0: Spin resolved HOPE science data.  Plasma moments from electrons >200 eV and ions >30 eV measured at apogee in alternate spin cadence.

Rules_of_use.0: Distribute freely, acknowledge original PI. Please contact PI before any publication or presentation of data.
